OL,3,CJersey looks to Guernsey for recycling
OL,4,Cinspiration
OL,6,FThere are calls in Jersey for the
OL,7,Fisland to adopt a waste management
OL,8,Fstrategy that moves away from
OL,9,Fincineration and towards a model of
OL,10,Frecycling similar to Guernsey's.
OL,12,FIt comes after a report by Policy
OL,13,FCentre Jersey revealed there is
OL,14,Fcurrently no plan for the future of
OL,15,Fhow the island deals with its waste.
