OL,3,CJersey looks to Guernsey for recycling
OL,4,Cinspiration
OL,6,FJersey's waste strategy currently
OL,7,Fdepends on La Collette Energy Recovery
OL,8,FFacility (ERF), which incinerates
OL,9,F105,000 tonnes of waste annually in
OL,10,Forder to produce electricity for
OL,11,F10,000 homes.
OL,13,FThe facility will need to be replaced
OL,14,Fin ten years' time - at an estimated
OL,15,Fcost of #250 million - and the
OL,16,Fgovernment has yet to decide what will
OL,17,Fhappen after that.
