OL,3,CJersey looks to Guernsey for recycling
OL,4,Cinspiration
OL,6,FThe report's author, Jennifer Bridge
OL,7,FMBE, says the community should see
OL,8,Fthis crossroads as an opportunity to
OL,9,Fshift towards a more environmental
OL,10,Fmodel - and argues a solution could be
OL,11,Ffound just across the water.
OL,13,FJennifer says her research was
OL,14,Ftriggered by the discovery that
OL,15,FGuernsey recycles 68% of their waste -
OL,16,Fwhereas Jersey's figure is around 35%.
OL,18,FGuernsey introduced a 'pay-as-you-
OL,19,Fthrow' initiative in 2019.
