OL,3,CJersey looks to Guernsey for recycling
OL,4,Cinspiration
OL,6,FConversely, Jennifer's report argues
OL,7,Fthe existence of the plant "undermines
OL,8,Freduction and recycling priorities"
OL,9,Fbecause the island relies on La
OL,10,FCollette to generate electricity - and
OL,11,Fthe facility requires waste in order
OL,12,Fto function.
OL,14,FWhilst kerbside recycling first came
OL,15,Fto in Jersey in 2006, progress is slow
OL,16,F- with three parishes still yet to
OL,17,Fintroduce it.
