OL,3,CJersey looks to Guernsey for recycling
OL,4,Cinspiration
OL,6,FBut the island's Minister for
OL,7,FInfrastructure, Constable Andy Jehan,
OL,8,Fsays the pay-as-you throw scheme is a
OL,9,Fviable option for Jersey too.
OL,11,F"We've seen how successful it's been
OL,12,Fin Guernsey and other jurisdictions",
OL,13,Fhe says.
OL,15,F"And what we're doing is looking to
OL,16,Fsee how we can increase the amount of
OL,17,Frecycling and reduce the amount of
OL,18,Fwaste".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/9
