OL,3,CJersey looks to Guernsey for recycling
OL,4,Cinspiration
OL,6,FHe adds that a significant amount of
OL,7,Fconsultation with key stakeholders
OL,8,Fwould be required before a scheme was
OL,9,Fintroduced, and it would not likely
OL,10,Fsee the light of day before next
OL,11,Fyear's general election.
OL,13,F"We'd certainly see more than 8, 12
OL,14,Fmonths to bring something like this in
OL,15,F- but we can't wait for the election
OL,16,Fbefore we start the discussions, we
OL,17,Fneed to start the discussions now", he
OL,18,Fsays.
